      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or GCI analysis demonstrates discretization error below 5% on QoI at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed (coarse/medium/fine: 2.1M/8.4M/33.6M cells). GCI for hemolysis index QoI is 3.8%, within the 5% acceptance threshold. Asymptotic range confirmed."
    },
