      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions are documented and sufficiently match simulation inputs for the validation activity.",
      "rationale": "FDA experimental dataset documents inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, and fluid properties. Simulation boundary conditions derived directly from published test protocol. Uncertainty in inlet conditions quantified and propagated."
